des: The Feel Good Project is a simple skill with a simple message. Mental health is a huge issue that effects millions of people. Sometimes all it takes to turn someone's day around, is to tell them that they matter. To hear that they are doing great. Or for someone to tell them that things will get better. The Feel Good Project is about spreading positivity to everyone. Because we all deserve to have good days. You can leave your voice message by going to https://littlevoicesproductions.com/feel-good-project
